With rotation (recommended)
===========================

1) Generate perfect crystal with good orientation
corresponding to dislocation orientation
	x // [110]
	z // [-112]
	y // [1-11]
and also rotate elastic constants

In directory 1_Dislo:
	babel input.dat

2) Generate dislocation
In directory 2_Dislo: 
	babel input.dat


Without rotation (for fun)
=========================
1) Generate perfect crystal keeping cubic axes
In directory 1_Dislo:
	babel input.dat

2) Generate dislocation
In directory 2_Dislo: 
	babel input.dat
